The paper focuses on text recognition in images using deep learning models, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of semantic information and sequence-to-sequence models also suggests a potential connection to natural language processing (cs.CL) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also mentions the use of deep learning techniques such as convolutional neural networks and recurrent neural networks, which are commonly used in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
